Here's an example of the following job going through the termination flow:
```python
import time

from dagster import job, op, resource


@resource
def some_resource_with_spindown(context):
    try:
        yield "foo"
    finally:
        context.log.info("Spinning down resource")


@op(required_resource_keys={"foo"})
def some_op():
    time.sleep(60)
    return 1



